    "body": "Yes I'm using go-ethereum. The abigen tool will use solc to generate the solidity abi from sol source files but this would be the first important tool that would be managed outside the go toolchain (e.g. go modules).\r\n\r\nI prototyped an example of how the solidity compiler might be wrapped up with the go tooling ecosystem to provide a convenient and reproducible means of relying on a particular version of the solc compiler.\r\n\r\n",
